i can tell you there are no mosquitos visible no midges no 
anything were extremely clean he said were ready to go 
later in the day however a short was detected in a heater 
cable in a strut that connects the shuttle to its huge fuel tank 
the heater prevents ice from forming on the strut when the tank is 
