police narcotics unit said of the pagers 
customers order drugs by telephoning a dealers pager and then 
punching in a phone number or a prearranged code police say the 
dealer responds by calling back or showing up with the drugs 
in the past minneapolis and st paul police regularly asked the 
telephone company to remove pay phones in druginfested areas or to 
