nations had a chance to write the final chapter in the horror 
story of the worlds drug epidemic if it fostered an 
international commitment to work together to end the drug crisis 
if this succeeded he said then we have sent the drug 
kingpins and dealers a warning they must heed or face certain doom 
their days are numbered 
we also will be sending a message to users that they bear 
responsibility in perpetuating the drug problem we must 
communicate to users that help is available to them but that they 
