<TEXT>
his mother was a maid in memphis tenn who 
brought books for him to read from the white homes where she 
worked today eddie n williams heads the joint center for 
political studies a research group playing an increasingly 
important role as blacks move into the political mainstream 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
eddie n williams is constantly on the phone 
these days fielding questions what with black politicians so much 
in the news 
is jesse jackson maintaining his hold on black voters 
how did l douglas wilder pull off his election as the first 
black governor of virginia 
how is the indictment of mayor marion barry playing among black 
