billion to help with the bat purchase 
to buy farmers axamidi was to borrow 225 billion from banks 
and 225 billion from goldsmith by giving him promissory notes 
goldsmith then was to sell the notes for cash 
while axamidi has an outstanding european record the 
leverage of this deal is such that it would endanger the farmers 
group of insurance companies insurance commissioner roxani 
gillespie said in a statement issued by her department 
