british takeover panel has said he must gain clearance for his 
plans for farmers in each of the nine states in which farmers 
operates an insurance company 
illinois idaho oregon and washington also have held hearings 
on the proposed takeover but have not announced decisions hearings 
began monday in texas insurance departments in arizona kansas and 
ohio have yet to set hearing dates 
